---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service | Happy House"
  description="Happy House terms of service."
>
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-[40px] font-bold text-navy">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing or using the Happy House website, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not access the website.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Services</h2>
          <p>Happy House provides search engine optimization and related digital marketing services for home services contractors. Service terms, deliverables, and pricing are agreed upon separately between Happy House and each client.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>The content, features, and functionality of this website are owned by Happy House and are protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about these terms, please contact us at hello@happyhouseseo.com.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-muted italic">[This is a placeholder terms of service. Replace with your legally reviewed terms before launch.]</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
